%spark

val assembler = new VectorAssembler().setInputCols(Array("AGE", "MTM_LTV", "INCENTIVE", "CREDIT_SCORE")).setOutputCol("features")
val df_filtered = df_clean1.filter($"MTM_LTV" > 0.0).filter($"INCENTIVE" > -1.0).filter($"CREDIT_SCORE" > 0).filter($"NEXT_STATUS" >= 0).filter($"NEXT_STATUS" <= 2)
val df_filtered2 = df_clean2.filter($"MTM_LTV" > 0.0).filter($"INCENTIVE" > -1.0).filter($"CREDIT_SCORE" > 0).filter($"NEXT_STATUS" >= 0).filter($"NEXT_STATUS" <= 2)
df_filtered.show()

val assembled = assembler.transform(df_filtered)
val assembled2 = assembler.transform(df_filtered2)

assembled.show()

%spark
val reduced = assembled.limit(10 * 1000)

val rf = new RandomForestClassifier().setLabelCol("NEXT_STATUS").setFeaturesCol("features").setNumTrees(12).setMaxDepth(10)
val model = rf.fit(reduced)
var rf_pred = model.transform(reduced) // This is totally in-sample, perhaps not ideal, do something better.
var rf_pred2 = model.transform(assembled2)

val lr = new LogisticRegression().setMaxIter(100).setRegParam(0.001).setElasticNetParam(0.001).setLabelCol("NEXT_STATUS").setFeaturesCol("features")
val lrModel = lr.fit(reduced)
var lr_pred = lrModel.transform(reduced) // This is totally in-sample, perhaps not ideal, do something better.
var lr_pred2 = lrModel.transform(assembled2)

// Unpack the probability vector to a more useful form, and compute useful entropies.
rf_pred = rf_pred.withColumn("prob_array",toArrUdf($"probability"))
rf_pred = rf_pred.withColumn("prob_p", $"prob_array"(0)).withColumn("prob_c", $"prob_array"(1)).withColumn("prob_3", $"prob_array"(2))
rf_pred = rf_pred.withColumn("actual_p", boolToNumber($"next_status" === 0)).withColumn("actual_c", boolToNumber($"next_status" === 1)).withColumn("actual_3", boolToNumber($"next_status" === 2))
rf_pred = rf_pred.withColumn("distEntropy", distH($"probability")).withColumn("rho", rho($"next_status", $"probability"))

lr_pred = lr_pred.withColumn("prob_array",toArrUdf($"probability"))

lr_pred = lr_pred.withColumn("actual_p", boolToNumber($"next_status" === 0)).withColumn("actual_c", boolToNumber($"next_status" === 1)).withColumn("actual_3", boolToNumber($"next_status" === 2))
lr_pred = lr_pred.withColumn("distEntropy", distH($"probability")).withColumn("rho", rho($"next_status", $"probability"))
